dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Map covers southwest land division of Western Australia.
Bar scale in miles, 100 miles = 85 mm.
Table of Comparative Wheat Yields (for all states, covering multiple years), legend showing approximate limits of rainfall.
Map shows area open for sale, area sold, area of England, waterways, various place names ("Dragon Rk.," "Pingaring Sp."), towns, roads, railroads, stations.
Above legends is Western Australia Department of Lands & Surveys seal.
